--------------------------------------------------------
Installation Instructions:

	-> Install dependencies

1 - sudo apt-get install cruft

	-> If a dependency message appears do the following

2 - sudo apt-get -f install 

	-> install the package in a different directory from the libera 
		default  (/opt/libera/bin/...)

3 - dpkg --instdir=${HOME}/EDM/libera-gui -i <PATH_TO_LIBERA_EPICS_GUI>/libera-epics-gui_2.2-52~r12582+4eBPM_i386.deb
